@startuml Deployment Overview
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam roundcorner 10

title Employee Management System - Deployment Overview

node "Development Environment" #LightBlue {
    [Local Docker Compose] as LocalDocker
    [Local PostgreSQL] as LocalDB
}

node "CI/CD Infrastructure" #LightGreen {
    [GitHub Actions] as GitHubActions
    [Jenkins] as Jenkins
    [Docker Hub] as DockerHub
}

node "Production Environment" #LightYellow {
    [Docker Host] as DockerHost
    [PostgreSQL Container] as ProdDB
    [Backend Container] as ProdBackend
    [Gateway Container] as ProdGateway
}

cloud "External" #LightCoral {
    [Users] as Users
    [GitHub] as GitHub
    [AWS Cloud] as AWS
}

Users --> ProdGateway : HTTPS
ProdGateway --> ProdBackend : HTTP (Internal)
ProdBackend --> ProdDB : JDBC

GitHub --> GitHubActions : Push/PR
GitHubActions --> Jenkins : CI Pass
Jenkins --> DockerHub : Build & Push
DockerHub --> DockerHost : Pull & Deploy

LocalDocker --> LocalDB : Development

note right of LocalDocker
  **Development:**
  - docker-compose up
  - Local testing
  - Hot reload
end note

note right of GitHubActions
  **CI Pipeline:**
  - Automated tests
  - Code quality
  - Build verification
end note

note right of Jenkins
  **CD Pipeline:**
  - Integration tests
  - Docker builds
  - Deployment automation
end note

note right of DockerHost
  **Production:**
  - Container orchestration
  - Health monitoring
  - Auto-restart
end note

@enduml

